column2: SELECT TOP # G.objID, G.ra, G.dec, s.specObjID, s.h_alpha_flux, s.h_alpha_flux_err, s.h_beta_flux, s.h_beta_flux_err, s.oiii_#_flux, s.oiii_#_flux_err, s.oiii_#_flux, s.oiii_#_flux_err, s.nii_#_flux, s.nii_#_flux_err, p.z, p.zErr FROM Galaxy as G JOIN GalSpecLine AS s ON G.specObjID = s.specObjID JOIN PhotoZ AS p ON G.objID = p.objID WHERE ( (u - r < = #) and (r - i < = #) and (r - z < = #) and (g - r > = r - i + #) and (u - r > = #* (r - z) ))
